KeysToEntries.story_4_1_000:
Got a hot tip
straight off the street…
KeysToEntries.story_4_1_001:
The White Comet of Akagi
lost to Akina’s 86…
KeysToEntries.story_4_1_002:
Hah?
You’re clueless.
Here’s what it means—
KeysToEntries.story_4_1_003:
Everything in the racing scene
just flipped.
KeysToEntries.story_4_1_004:
Bastard…
that’s what I was gonna say…
KeysToEntries.story_4_1_005:
Cut the chatter—
we’re racing today.
Line up.
